4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning bootcamp designed for beginners. Over a duration of 16 weeks, participants will engage in three classes weekly, with a maximum class size of 12. The course covers essential skills such as Python, SQL, and statistics, alongside practical applications of various machine learning algorithms. Instructors include experts like Sayyed Nezhadi and Francesco Pugliese, each with extensive backgrounds in AI and machine learning. No prior experience is needed, and content is available in English and Spanish. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop